3572959"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573572959"&gt;租金向升持續，個別地區租盤更屢創新高租金成交。中原地產元朗副區域營業經理王勤學表示，暑假旺季期間，租金明顯快速上升，近期租賃市場頻錄破頂成交。其中元朗朗屏8號新錄1座低層B室租務，單位實用面積246方呎，屬開放式間隔，原本月租叫價13,000元，日前獲從事IT行業的專業人士議價後，以12,200元承租，平均實用呎租49.6元，創屋苑呎租新高紀錄。單位業主於2016年5月以278.3萬元一手買入物業，持貨約9年，是次出租可享5.3厘租金回報。&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E9%25A0%2582-%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%25B1%258F8%25E8%2599%259F%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%2591%258E%25E7%25A7%259F%25E6%2592%25B250%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25BF1.7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%25A7%259F%25E8%25B3%2583%2F588588&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=9f81033cce4059222e5032216f4a3e80&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/元朗租金 ... .7萬創新高-二手樓租賃/588588&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32005424&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1401830384689bf41a6221b4_77749120"/><published>2025-08-12T16:11:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f63b8b5b2aa33a88e8c21b258800657d</id><title>回流香港買家執平貨 1998萬馬鞍山迎海四房 上手8年帳蝕兩成</title><updated>2025-08-12T16:39:24+08:00</updated><author><name>elsababa</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-12T16:39:24+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573573243"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573573243"&gt;醒目仔&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="60" src="https://www.discuss.co